* [[Kushyar Gilani]], Persian mathematician and [[geographer]] (d. [[1029]])
* [[Mahmud of Ghazni]], emir of the [[Ghaznavids|Ghaznavid Empire]] (d. [[1030]])
* [[Abbot Oliba|Oliba]], Spanish count and [[bishop]] (approximate date)

