* [[Ibn Rumahis|Muhammad ibn Rumahis]], Umayyad admiral 
* [[Ordgar, Ealdorman of Devon|Ordgar]], English [[ealdorman]] and advisor
* [[Qian Hongzong]], king of [[Wuyue]] (approximate date)
* [[Ziri ibn Manad]], founder of the [[Zirid dynasty|Zirid Dynasty]]

